so to get  near  we simply require 
that  have monodromy  on a counterclockwise circle around .
What is more subtle is to define the boundary condition at  and we propose to do it by
analytically continuing  via "Wick rotation" to the line
, where the asymptotic behavior of the solutions is purely
oscillatory and hence one can really pick out a particular solution by specifying
its asymptotics.

In the limit where  is almost pure imaginary, the line 
